WEBVTT

1
00:29:26.830 --> 00:29:28.160 
他在观看演习啊
He's watching the maneuvers.

2
00:29:28.160 --> 00:29:29.660 
警署总督呢？
And the Police Commissioner?

3
00:29:29.660 --> 00:29:31.070 
我知道了，他在监视维利·勃兰特
I see. He's watching Willy Brandt.

4
00:29:31.070 --> 00:29:33.230 
那警察局谁管？
So who's minding the store?

5
00:29:33.230 --> 00:29:35.000 
打到伯恩那边去了吗？
What about the call to Bonn?

6
00:29:35.000 --> 00:29:37.670 
大使回华盛顿参加咨询会去了？
Our ambassador is back in Washington for consulation?

7
00:29:37.670 --> 00:29:39.270 
进来，进来，我等会跟你说
Come in, come in. I'll be right with you.

8
00:29:39.270 --> 00:29:40.640 
打到华盛顿的国务院去
Get me Washington, the State Department...

9
00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:41.880 
谁接都行
whoever answers

10
00:29:41.880 --> 00:29:44.010 
迪安·拉斯克，迪安·艾奇逊，是个叫迪安的都行
Dean Rusk, Dean Acheson, Dean

11
00:29:44.010 --> 00:29:45.250 
如果那边也没人接
And if you have no luck there...

12
00:29:45.250 --> 00:29:46.880 
就打给乔治亚州的塔尔马吉参议员
get me Senator Talmadge of Georgia.

13
00:29:46.880 --> 00:29:50.150 
如果他也不在，就试试打给国家广播公司的亨特利和布林克利
If he isn't in, try Huntley

14
00:29:51.020 --> 00:29:52.290 
斯嘉丽！
Scarlett!

15
00:29:52.290 --> 00:29:54.190 
你这么激动干嘛？
What's all the excitement?

16
00:29:54.190 --> 00:29:56.460 
哦，没事
Oh, nothing.

17
00:29:56.460 --> 00:29:57.990 
你刚才把我们都吓死了！
You just scared the hell out of us!

18
00:29:57.990 --> 00:29:59.060 
你还好吗？
You all right?

